    "description": "This carb smart recipe replaces half the white rice for cauliflower rice. Stopover in Indonesia for mussels in a sweet and sour broth spiked with sambal oelek. Serve with sticky rice and toasted coconut flakes for a masterpiece in every mouthful. Mari makan.",
